org.linqs.psl.reasoner.term.streaming

Class StreamingInitialRoundIterator<T extends ReasonerTerm>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.reasoner.term.streaming.StreamingInitialRoundIterator<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterator<T>, StreamingIterator<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DCDStreamingInitialRoundIterator, SGDStreamingInitialRoundIterator

    public abstract class StreamingInitialRoundIterator<T extends ReasonerTerm>
extends Object
implements StreamingIterator<T>
    Iterate over all the terms that come up from grounding. On this first iteration, we will build the term cache up from ground rules and flush the terms to disk.
